{"tid":1796801,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"反修例風波「示警」譚耀宗：23條立法有逼切性","createTime":"2019-12-25T01:16:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-25T03:24:10.000Z","uid":90397,"like":3,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"55976fc7047cb4cfbfb296d76ab789f7969826eb","tid":1796801,"uid":90397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T01:16:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xoJaHe8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxoJaHe8.png&h=5e29c3c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n反修例黑暴事件持續了半年，香港社會大受打擊！全國人大常委譚耀宗認為，今次風波反映本港更有逼切性就基本法23條立法，不過他亦明言，相信難度或比修訂逃犯條例更高。<br />\n23條真的是洪水猛獸？澳門立了23條後風平浪靜，反之沒立法的香港，反而因有了這漏洞而出現反修例黑暴事件！譚耀宗講得好！23條立法絕對有逼切性！支持即like！"},{"pid":"6983cf0017a155f200048c521e30bfe55d235ab8","tid":1796801,"uid":45087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T01:43:36.000Z","msg":"cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲想搞多鑊"},{"pid":"03270cc111f8cadb774484418259300710885928","tid":1796801,"uid":161726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T01:45:41.000Z","msg":"支持支持支持，歡迎民建聯送個頭出黎同林鄭一齊推２３條<br />\n申請永續運動"},{"pid":"33866e3eaf338d375478661a9241dbf405c51fb3","tid":1796801,"uid":53815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T02:09:12.000Z","msg":"港共真係好唔想場運動停<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16f4ba943a9a25f998fc67d2c7869d769b6df686","tid":1796801,"uid":101945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T02:13:29.000Z","msg":"澳門咁平靜<br />\n中國咁強大 全部非民主派走啦 <br />\n永遠不要到香港生活"},{"pid":"ca168f785a50aafbd83f74660cac7afbff8c9385","tid":1796801,"uid":281189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"33866e3eaf338d375478661a9241dbf405c51fb3","tid":1796801,"uid":53815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T02:09:12.000Z","msg":"港共真係好唔想場運動停<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" clas